      "============================================================\n",
      "Scenario A: Price Spike / Tail Stress  (ν=3, N_rep=500)\n",
      "============================================================\n",
      "\n",
      "Primary diagnostics (expected HIGH power):\n",
      "  AD rej rate  — price : 1.000\n",
      "  AD rej rate  — temp  : 1.000\n",
